About

Started as in "Dead enders" by Ayaan Eusufzai in 2018, making/publishing books that are sadly no longer available, then going to "Nagida", which was making/publishing music, all that happened in 2019 and then it expanded to a game called "Minecraft", becoming EARTHITOC CORPORATION. It was a simple realm made in Minecraft bedrock, a simple creative realm community and now it started making servers and became known for making the earthitoc Minecraft server and now earthitoc corporationis gev x. which leads us to the present day.
